In its "warning of risk, society points out that, in relation to the activity of the guard Hungarian, the greatest risk policy is already" in the short term ethnic clashes aggressive may occur following the worsening of ethnic tension already existing between the population and gypsy not gypsy Hungary.
The research institute went on to say that the political strategy of the guard Hungarian aimed probably has cause this situation is the main reason.
As they say, this is due to one of the main shortcomings of Hungarian political actors: "actors public have passed the public debate on the matter of Roma representatives of political groupings radical and extremes that have a political strategy based on the dispute between gypsies and Hungarians.
The Probleme is aggravated, the normal dialogue becomes impossible, the extremists are strengthened and the arrival of aggressive conflict is more likely, they say.
Indeed, according to the research institute, under the effect of the increased attention of media Hungarian and international activity guard Hungarian "has deteriorated significantly the image of Hungary abroad, in particular on the confidence in the stability and the democratic maturity of the country.
They remind us that, following has greater publicity has given the reorganisation of radical groups and extremes right Hungarian since the autumn of 2006, numerous associations were set up in Hungary since the summer of 2007 is giving the name of' national association self-defense ".
