The emphasis on the Caractere civil and status association serves only that has avoided Pieges legal registration of these associations to the Court but they are also a political strategy.
The analysis indicates that the activity of the guard Hungarian is a factor which increases the risk in relation to the neighbourly relations.
"In recent months, many countries neighbouring cite the Hungarian guard as a potential source of risk and politicians ultranationalists of some neighbouring countries wish to justify their policy Anti-Hungarian with reference has the Constitution guard Hungarian.
This influence the political stability of the region, have added.
According to the research institute, the Constitution guard Hungarian is not a single Phénomene in Central Europe, the political risks have increased on the region as a whole.
As they say, the operation of the guard Hungarian looks like, for example, has the activity of the National Guard Bulgarian whose constitution has been declared by the Bulgarian national Union (Bnu) Aout in 2007.
The many problems of Roma that have occurred in a district of Sofia (Kraszna Poljana) are at the origin of the Constitution of the Bulgarian guard.
