The Czech companies will be able to obtain around 100 billion kronor in the framework of the programme enterprise and innovation.
The transport sector will benefit the most, up to 150 billion.
The programme transport is the most important and the operational programme is up to 22% of the financial resources that the Czech Rép. can achieve in the framework of these projects.
The money will be responsible for an increase in the budget from the bottom national transport infrastructure which will manage next year a sum of payments billion kronor.
The programme enterprise and innovation, for SMEs and entrepreneurs, must be used to obtain financial resources to encourage innovation within the company.
Companies should obtain financial resources for the introduction of new technologies, research in the industry, but also for the introduction of new methods of management more effective.
