There are four years, the Court has proven that Geneva Alemán was regularly money from the government to Auditors of foreign companies in Panama.
It was fictitious companies and the accounts actually belonged to the members of his family and closest supporters.
Some of this money has gone into the funds that Geneva Alemán had created to finance his election campaign in 2001.
We adopted the budget
That is the way it is.
The state budget has been adopted.
Why is this budget is exceptional?
