The driving licence is, in his view, a document that people can decide whether they wish to have or not.
It is not as with the identity card, which must be valid without exceptions.
People want more lead should put their driving licence.
We need only the make or send them to the city.
Driving licences issued between 1964 and 1993 cease to be valid at the end of the year.
However, the drivers of vehicles are also forced to renew gradually other types of driving licences.
