The Congress approved the implementation of the MiFID, which entered into force on 1 November
At the same time to its Parliamentary formality, which ended today with the vote of the Congress of the amendments incorporated in the draft in the Senate, the government has submitted to a public hearing the regulation which develop the new law, with a view to its entry into force before the year end.
The representatives of the various groups agreed to highlight the efforts made by the Members and senators to negotiate and make better regulation designed to ensure the protection of investors and to regulate in detail the activity of bodies for markets operate effectively.
The MiFID, which changes the law of market values, means the modernisation of financial markets, at a time when it strengthens the protection of investors, improving the powers of the leaders of the national Commission of the securities market (CNMV) and promote cooperation between the various European Union leaders.
The new regulation will pay services consultation financial reasons both social specialist that to natural or legal persons and creates a new type of financial services (Esis), the companies consultation financial (Afi), merging companies of values, the values agencies and companies asset managers.
Moreover, it increases the number of systems for the implementation of operations on financial instruments, so that it is possible to add to the markets secondary Réglemantés the negotiating multilateral systems and systems of internationalisation of orders, which front compete with the current managers of stock market.
The law also obliges companies to disclose investment services market information on the key aspects of his profile case, to exposure to risk and forms of risk management and it forces them to keep a register of all operations they do, in order to facilitate control by the CNMV.
Through the Committee of economy of Congress, several amendments have been added, which highlights Titularisées that debts will be considered a financial instrument "complex" in view of its high risk for the investor, who has shown with what happened with the debt of mortgages American high risk (sub-prime).
In addition, they have taken advantage of the transposition of the direction has the opportunity to define legally functions that the graduates economy may have 30 years after that in 1977, has been approved, the Royal Decree which defines the functions professional reserved for economists.
For its part, the Senate has incorporated the creation of new figures in the financial sector, such as the Ombudsman, which will work for a company, which will require the authorisation of the CNMV and which will lend its services marketing of products and to attract new customers to different investment firms at the same time.
The index of consumer prices harmonised increases of five tenths in November, up to 4.1%
This indicator, which is used according to Eurostat to incorporate the calculation of the rate of inflation in the European Union, provides an assessment of the evolution of prices in Spain during the month of November.
Its publication responds to the policy of Eurostat and of the European Central Bank (ECB) by offering comparable data over time and in quality to those produced in the United States.
The indicator is calculated using the same procedure as that used for the index of consumer prices harmonised, but using different methods of statistical Modelisation to estimate the information Surlaquelle it is has not yet at the moment of publication.
The Ine pointed out that the information provided by the indicator is only indicative, because it does not necessarily coincide with the given final which will be shown on 14 December.
