A colleague passes the information on the introduction in the code of criminal offences on the downloads on the Internet:
a. the downloading a song would be a crime punishable by a sentence of six months to a year.
On the other hand, the theft in a shop of CDs worth less than EUR 400, is seen only as a fault (Article 623.1).
B. theft in a shop worth up to EUR 1, 000 is already considered a crime, but the trouble is lower than that imposed for the downloading (Article 234 of the penal code).
C. if you kill a car and you go the 40 hours after the sentence is lower than that imposed for the downloading (an article 244.1).
D. It is less serious to take part in a fight that to participate in the trafficking of compact discs.
Take part in a fight tumultuous means a sentence of three months to a year (Article 154 of the criminal code) and the trafficking of CDs would mean a sentence of six months to two years
(Rule 270 of the criminal code).
E. sexual harassment at work is considered less serious than download a film, according to Article 184.2 of the penal code.
F. distribution of films protected by copyright and without permission of authors is more punishment that the distribution of pornographic material to minors (article 186).
