What assurance I agree?
motor insurance, which covers the driver in the face of possible claims, involves expenditure important will depend on various factors, such as age, gender, age of the driving licence, marital status, the type of vehicle to ensure or the use of the Internet, among other things.
Having a car that is the main.
There ES that, Escoger El Seguro of Automóvil Adecuado ES Incluso' Difícil that Elegir El Gruma of Vehículo.
And that is that, choose motor insurance proper, is even more difficult than choose the model of the vehicle.
The car insurance is an agreement between an insurance company and the insurer.
This compromise materializes by a contract of insurance, which states that the company receives the value of the premium paid and in exchange it becomes responsible for the obligation to pay compensation in the event of a disaster.
The premium is the price of insurance, which establishes taking into account various factors, such as age, gender, age of the driving licence, marital status, the type of vehicle to ensure or the Usageque we in fact, among others.
Insurance companies set their prices according to the statistics, so that more likely to have an accident is high, the more popular to pay is high.
That is why the people over 25 years and women have to pay premiums lower, since the statistics show that these Persones have a rate lower claims of their care.
In the same way, using of censuses, companies have concluded that married people tend to have fewer accidents that drivers single.
The use of the vehicle that affect the frequency, and therefore the likelihood of having an accident.
By increasing the frequency the likely increase.
There are many variables that insurers take into account in setting the price of the premium.
That is why, that the driver must study the situation in choosing the motor insurance which is best suited to its profile.
We would have to express here the variables at the time of the most significant choose one or other type of insurance, so that it, in addition to adapt to the characteristics of the insurer, it offers a reasonable price.
The young people under 25 years have to deal with various disadvantages when a contract with insurance accessible at a price, as can be the weak experience in the conduct and the age of the driving licence.
Although the ideal to be assured insurance is at risk, other options more economic exist.
The drivers more far-sighted can opt for any risk insurance frankly, so that they get the insurance coverage to any risk but at a price more accessible.
This form of convention means that the customer pays a part of the amount of the sinister.
"The part of the amount of the claim that the customer pays will be established on the basis of the value of the premium, which will be higher over the amount will be weak", specifies Luis Noguera, the head in Spain of first Europa, Ombudsman insurance online.
Another option is the assurance to third enlarged, so that the customer can assure the protection in order to deal with the damage caused to third parties, but by those caused on its own car.
Moreover, it would be covered against theft, fires and the loss of the vehicle.
A Council.
If you are minor 25 years Essaies be careful and to avoid accidents as far as possible, because it has implications for the subsidy, can reduce the price of insurance in the future.
A subsidy is a reduction in the basic tariff that has the company.
On the contrary, a penalty is an increase in the basic tariff.
"Subsidies and sanctions will depend on the company and profit.
If the company has had a good year it will be able to afford to increase subsidies', clarifies Noguera.
Beyond 25 years it becomes easier for drivers at the time of a contract with insurance, since the rate of accidents is reduced thanks to the experience gained.
It is for this reason that it is better to choose any risk insurance frankly.
"Normally young people can not benefit from the experience gained in advance after an accident", provides the director of the European company in Spain and adds that the majority of accidents occur during the second year of conduct, once past the' fear of amateur'.
However, if the customer is married but has not yet children that it is better to negotiate insurance to any risk, the Momento that the economic situation allows us to do so.
Marriages with children are viewed by insurers as people with the rate of accidents the lowest, because the increases will be weaker.
In this case the best insurance would be insurance at any risk frankly (that can be 300 Euros), or insurance to third enlarged from the third year of life of the vehicle when the insured person has a high level of subsidy.
"They conduct a more relaxed and they have greater purchasing power to afford the luxury to take on a greater proportion of exemptions", judge Luis Noguera.
For pensioners insurance to any risk frankly is better (being it of EUR 150), or a Asurance to third enlarged when the insurer has a high level of subsidy.
It must be said that motor insurance is something important, not only because it covers the driver against any claims, but also because it represents an important expenditure, and that is why it is vital to study properly insurance which suits us the most in our personal situation.
