At this level, France and Luxembourg play an important role in the education system of the Saarland system, which is placed fifth in the monitor training institute for the German economy in Cologne.
And, by tradition, colleges and universities cooperate closely with the neighbouring countries.
The university was founded in Saarbrücken in 1948 by the French.
So far, the students have the chance to complete their studies by a double or triple a diploma.
Witness the Quotitée high of 15.6% of foreign students.
The Saarland led by elsewhere too children in the country until the colleges and universities in number higher than the average - many of them without a diploma of the gymnasium.
