The history of the three American war reporters, who determine trail for the high war criminal' The Fox', could have perhaps become, with another director and another scriptwriter (both both Richard wrote) on another occasion, a new "Apocalypse Now".
Because the stories are the same so striking: two male will in small team in the forest, to do something that the military can not do and for both male, it becomes a trip to the madness.
One of the reasons for the failure of "the hunting party" is that it leaves simply not Simon hunt be the cynical deserted with a heart, as presented to us at the beginning.
No, the script must also give it a romantic adventure with a Bosnian murdered.
Then "the hunting party" becomes definitively bad, when the delay, in the space of the last five minutes, by a process speeded up, succeeds in NATO, the CIA and all the premium hunters of the world have failed in five years: catch the war criminal and leave in a just revenge the Bosnian Muslims.
It is so bad that we should seize the International Court in The Hague of crimes against the logic film.
In this case, the film has a concern human too deep.
It wants to denounce that Karadzic and Mladic are still at large, and it suspect the Americans and the French (here they have to be exceptionally agreement) not lead hunting fairly intensive because of political agreements secret.
But the well-intentioned and the villain this time are so similar that a famous Poême of Brecht comes to the idea.
That speaks with a wooden mask a demon Asian working on the table of Poête: "compassionate, I see no front swollen, as is clear: Fatiguant to be bad."
Films such as "the hunting party" have exactly such head Tumescentes, but that implies the Fatiguant to be good.
The problem is not limited to the kind of films on the war in the Balkans.
Recently, it has been reported in this newspaper that all Hollywood films on Iraq were major flops.
We can add: there has never been a good films on South Africa.
What is true every time: when a star lagging behind on a trouble spot or on a minefield, then it leads to something like "Rangoon" with Patricia Arquette, "Jenseits go Grenzen" with Angelina beautiful "or" Blutdiamanten "with Leonardo Dicaprio.
It is possible that all these conflicts are simply too close in time.
In any case, decades have always gone before Hollywood can turn a good film on the Holocaust with "the list of".
Some films are even mature, those who are now classic works on Vietnam "the deer hunter," "Apocalypse Now" or "stop metal Jackett" have by no means been unanimous in their time as masterpieces.
But perhaps we know today also simply too on the conflicts of the world, where every massacre is directly on two screens at the same time at home,
And this pleased to Scénaristes the lack of sensitivity they need to tell good stories.
"To be or not to be" or "the dictator" are in fact become as good also because Lubtisch and Chaplin did not know yet how the Nazi regime dominated really.
