Von Beust harvest criticism for the cancellation of traditions.
The decline of the mayor of with the application of Hamburg for the summer Olympics met in politics and the economy to fierce criticism.
Many want to continue to fight for the games on the edge of the water.
But von Beust call for realism in the assessment of opportunities.
The main director of the Chamber of Commerce of Hamburg, Hans-jörg Schmidt-trenz, described Wednesday a departure as "bad for the local economy".
In recent times, no other project has deployed so many forces in the city of motivation that the idea of traditions.
"Without this objective, the momentum Politico-sportif could not have been maintained under the same measures".
Schmidt-trenz urge the Senate not to bury the project, but to find a new starting point in the longer term, "which takes as its starting point another agenda changed".
The Mayor Ole von Beust not on Wednesday at its previous declarations, that the ambitions Olympic Hamburg were unrealistic at least until the year 2000/2028.
"It's not Hamburg who decides to applications to the traditions, but the Federation German Olympic sport" said von Beust to Welt online.
It refers to the decision of the Federation expected at the beginning of December Sport, on the application of Munich for the winter games of 2018.
This preference means for us, that, in the time that we anticipated until 2000/2028 until then, we will have no chance. "
However, the dream is not definitively a thing of the past, said von Beust.
The sports federation of Hamburg (Hsb) lamented the statements of Beust.
Of this the impression would be given that Hamburg no longer wishes to apply for the Olympic Games in the next 25 years.
"It is too early to ignore an opportunity, ground projects already now", said on Wednesday President of Hsb Günter Ploß.
Abandoning the application would be more at odds with the statements by the leader of the Senate on the occasion of reception in the plenary assembly of the Federation of German universities of sport.
There, von Beust would have described the candidacy of Hamburg to Universiades 2015 as being "not a substitute" the Olympic Games in Hamburg.
The Federation of universities of sport was first in the past weeks Hamburg nominated as candidate city.
The SPD fraction of the mayor has criticized the Senate for not using this valuable time in the construction of housing in Hamburg.
"The development of small Grasbrook has been rejected by the Senate for years because he has played the card of traditions and ruled out the construction of housing," said the delegates of the SPD Carola Veit and Jan Quast.
While the SPD has always demanded for the small Grasbrook a plan integrated into the traditions and subsequent uses of housing, the CDU would have relied solely on the "factor event".
's candidacy for the Summer Olympic Games in 2012 would for its part raised in Hamburg much enthusiasm.
Hamburg had, however, broken against Leipzig.
It is not the coffers of Warhols.
That linking the concepts Sweden and cash in wood, think Ikea, but not to Andy Warhol.
Or?
At the moment, funds wooden manufactured in Sweden cast of shadows on the list of works of Warhol.
Many of the ninety Brillo-boxs type of "Stockholm' catalogued there are counterfeiting.
After the Swedish newspaper "Expressen" has questioned the authenticity of a few months ago Brillo-boxs of the year of 1968 Andy Warhol, the research of internal Moderna Museet Stockholm result today a result Désenchanteur: the six "Brillo-boxes", including the former director of the museum Pontus Hulten gave in 1995 to Moderna Museet, are copies, and many of the other hundreds of Brillo-boxen type of "Stockholm", circulating on the international market of art.
History is fairly, a disconcerting sequence of artistic production and Curatoriques.
In 1964, Warhol created in New York its first "Brillo-boxes", funds wooden painted, based on the design of Rouge-bleu-blanc boxes of soap powder "Brillo".
An exhibition of his work Moderna Museet presented in 1968, with the agreement of Warhol - hundreds of funds Brillo made of cardboard: they came from outside (for financial reasons) by Warhol, but had been delivered directly to the factory Cartonnage Brillo.
It was not of works of art, but rather of their models, samples of exposure.
At the same time, Warhol had authorised in 1968 to produce a few coffers wooden Brillo in Sweden, which were not exposed to the Moderna Museet.
Witnesses of the time today talking about some fifteen coffers wooden which at the time would be right inflows in the history of art and auctions, as Brillo-boxes original of Andy Wahrol permitted, with the Appelation' type Stockholm ".
Some of them have achieved in the auctions more than 100 000 dollars.
The problem now is that the legendary director of the museum Pontus Hultén claimed, wrongly, as recently as about a hundred coffers wooden had been produced and exposed in Sweden in 1968, that Warhol would then pass.
In truth, the 105 funds Hultén have been produced in Malmö only in 1990, for an exhibition in St Petersburg.
On that date, Warhol was already death for three years.
Lars Byström, leader of the Conservative Moderna Museet, has examined, in addition to six Brillo-boxes museum, three other of private collections Suedoises, including two have been Confectionnées in Stockholm in 1968: their panels Stratifiés were first printed and Poncés, then it has been applied with a them of oil paint white.
The texture copies which date from 1990 reveals that the painting has been directly applied without layer on the panels Stratifiés, with a scroll of paint, most of it is not an oil paint, but a Acrylique.
"These funds have not been authorised by the artist and should be removed from the official list of Brillo-boxes of Andy Warhol" suggests, the director of the Moderna Museet, Lars Nittve: "if the' Andy Warhol art authentication board' in New York is not just another decision, the Moderna Museet classified the six funds in its collection as copies / material exposure."
Already in July the authentication board has, of course, announced it into on the "serious accusations" that will be raised in the case of funds soap powder.
But since we psychotic there a Inéxorable silence.
The soldiers rebels of Manila abandon
In the Philippines, the soldiers rebels abandon, the same people who had entrenched in a hotel in Manila, and which had demanded the withdrawal of President Gloria Macapagal Arroyo.
The head Antonio Trillanes, which accused the President of corruption and electoral fraud, has told reporters in the hotel that it can not respond to any bloodshed.
The soldiers faithful to power shortly before had stormed the hotel with gas Lacrimogène.
The two dozen soldiers had dug for hours in the building.
About half of them were held on Wednesday before the courts because of an attempted coup d' état missed in 2003 - among them Trillanes.
It during the hearing to overshadow suddenly with about 30 supporters.
The military police, which should normally monitor, had apparently deserted for it and had joined the mutiny.
They define in the hotel Peninsula and demanded the withdrawal of President Gloria Macapagal Arroyo.
The troops fair to power Bouclèrent the sector around the hotel respectable.
President Convoqua urgent session of the security cabinet.
The advisor for national security Norberto González doomed the action of soldiers.
"The people have had enough," said Trillanes.
"We call on the people to join us".
The general Danilo Lim, who control before the unit elites of scouts Rangers, said that other units of the army wanted shortly join the March.
Critics of the regime had called in a large demonstration against the President on Wednesday.
His government is surrounded for months by accusations of corruption.
The finance district of Manila was already since 2003 the scene of the attempted mutiny of some 200 Members of the army against Arroyo.
The insurgency Brisa nearly 24 hours after the refusal of the army to join.
Since 1986 there have been at least seven attempts of coup against democratically elected governments in the Philippines.
United Internet is becoming a main shareholder of Versatel.
United Internet has ensured participation of more than 20% of the society of telecommunications Versatel.
The average price for action is 14,46 euros, as the society's on Wednesday.
Only 20,05 per cent of social capital would be held.
We had already previously speculated on a takeover.
The option would remain open to further increase the participation in Versatel.
With this step we are trying to speed up the consolidation of the German market of Dsl, gave United Internet.
Just before, assumptions had already been made on a Wednesday entry, after the Bank Berenberg has increased its participation in the network operator of Düsseldorf of 5% to 15,1 per cent.
The Institute of credit from the money only for a third part, whoppers on the market.
The day before, united Internet had already acquired participation by almost 10% in society mobile phone Drillisch.
As part of a capital increase, Drillisch has placed on the stock exchange 17.4 million new actions worth 106,4 million euros.
United Internet has bought 5,15 million for 31,1 million euros.
Moreover, the companies have opened negotiations about cooperation in the marketing of products Dsl and mobile telephony.
"We Renforcons our partnership", explained a spokesman for United Internet.
The two companies based in society participation MSP to absorb competitor Freenet.
At the moment, the two companies want to be happy with their participation of 10% in Freenet, and not to make use of their right to take 18,49% additional among Freenet, says United Internet on Thursday.
The two companies leave all options open, however, in particular to increase the participation in its Freenet, it has been learned.
The negotiations between United Internet and Freenet on a strategic partnership had ended in Mid-October.
The poker still unpredictable on Freenet which has been going on for months is part of the consolidation of the German market telecoms.
Freenet had at the end of the third quarter 2.9 million customers bound by a contract mobile phone and 1.27 million customers Dsl and subscriptions complete.
The holding of United Internet and Drillisch had until now a direct participation in Freenet of 6,01 per cent.
It has now been agreed that Drillisch bring some 4% extra.
The right to buy the 18,49% of society investment Vatas had already been decided in August.
